重睇啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點知未來老婆Moka極力反對在海外結婚，堅持要在香港註冊，目的是為了要盡快得到居港權。 </span>"},{"pid":"10e763779093a9a15aea666642d165830432c340","tid":177941,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"城城身家<br />\n拎美國加拿大澳洲護照0難度"},{"pid":"01eecddc53b347498260fe5388e3f6779b9e97e9","tid":177941,"uid":59242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:34:40.000Z","msg":"娶左咪撚帶返黎香港 大陸雞"},{"pid":"bda47e3e8127514d30f2fa8e08fc2a583049f89e","tid":177941,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"留明睇離婚"},{"pid":"755216a3e52e1df2702fcc3b2135cc288e7a0d1b","tid":177941,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾大陸雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係城城就係婚約度寫明唔會分身家同兒子有撫養權"},{"pid":"4d63feb042ddfc256d85147d7b9197ab5648fab9","tid":177941,"uid":52234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:40:39.000Z","msg":"懵撚城城"},{"pid":"eb964bfdc74bc508f216de94cd0ab6da6ea4a932","tid":177941,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:43:15.000Z","msg":"大陸臭雞"},{"pid":"ac64f2026e1df2daec17f56b2a7089cf306e69cd","tid":177941,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:53:58.000Z","msg":"又係貪居港權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1417bbbf10cdbc690f2a7cfbb5c1e40690ef1be","tid":177941,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"條大陸妹講就講想盡快要居港權，實際9成9係怕係大陸/美國註冊，到離婚嗰陣分得唔多。有錢既大陸人根本唔希罕黎香港住。"},{"pid":"d39be8de9ffd7ad3e2523f0d8f25fee83682f493","tid":177941,"uid":37661,"like"